Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:36.15,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(1050,595)}Nightmare\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to have others quickly\Nunderstand you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.63,0:01:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,first you must get closer\Nto their spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, when calling people\Nby their names,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.73,0:01:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it is impersonal to call people\Nusing "san" or "kun."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You will never get closer\Nto them like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.26,0:01:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You might first try taking the plunge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and call people by\Ntheir first name only...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,or try using a nickname or\Nterm of endearment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that, others will feel much\Nmore familiar about you... as a special person...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What...? Isn't that Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Make-Out Paradise is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come looking for a book\Nof paintings or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you read books, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So even Sai has quite\N{\i1}a human side to him, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto and I were just on our way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to visit Kakashi Sensei in the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi...Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on Team Kakashi too,\Nso you should meet him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Revenge is everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I can carry out my revenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it's no concern of mine what\N{\i1}happens to me, or to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if I can obtain the power\N{\i1}to accomplish that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}by giving my body to Orochimaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then I'll give him as much of\N{\i1}this life of mine as he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can see it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is your unknown power, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who would've thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you'd have something like\N{\i1}this inside of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I have that dream...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Sai's with you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I bumped into him at the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...and here I was working out\Nmy plan to walk with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,just the two of us,\Nlike we were on a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've got the time to be\Ndoing that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you should be studying up\Non Ninjutsu or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Study, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you guys even go to\Na stuffy place like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You should train your mind a little\Nand not just your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really an idiot, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it... Sakura is calling\N{\i1}Naruto only by his first name...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's harsh, Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Naruto, S-Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you guys include me\Nin the conversation, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Well, I read in a book...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,about how to open up to\Nother people right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the book, it said to call people\Nby their first names only
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and to use nicknames and\Nterms of endearment...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It said if I did that there would\Nbe a sense of friendliness
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'd be able\Nto get along right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you're concerned\Nabout stuff like that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what you were doing\Nin the library...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And... I was thinking about nicknames and\N terms of endearment for you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't really come up\Nwith anything good...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll just call you guys by\Njust your first names for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe Sai would think\N{\i1}so seriously about us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to think about stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It just happens naturally!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,For nicknames or terms\Nof endearment,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you should just say that\Nperson's character trait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,For example,\Nif you're talking about Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot Naruto! Or moron Naruto!\NOr something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura, you're taking things\Ntoo far with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get it...A person's character trait...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe this is Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's totally different from\N{\i1}when I first met him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to stare\Nat me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I've got the hang of it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai, you're really taking things\Ntoo far with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura, why'd you have to\Nhit me, too...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... You're the new team member.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai, was it? Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura, come here for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two are hurt...\NDid they fight or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be no stretch of the imagination\Nwith someone hot-tempered like Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, nothing happened at all...\NWe're all getting along fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...Then I guess it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is Kakashi Hatake, {\i1}the one rumored about\N{\i1}in the Anbu Black Ops Training Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi Sensei...\NAbout our previous mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about everything\Nfrom Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,About Sasuke, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, he'll soon be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't bring Sasuke back\Nwith the power I have now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gotten too powerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, you just have to get\Nmore powerful, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But...the speed of Sasuke's development\Nwas extraordinary even in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When I asked Lady Tsunade,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,she said there's a possibility they're using Forbidden Jutsu and perhaps drugs in his training...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And they've got Kabuto with them, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's probably no way to find out,\Nin a book like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,how people who conduct\Nexperiments on humans think...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we just have to\Nrapidly get more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think I was just lying here\Nnot thinking about anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about that the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And...I figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this approach is\Nsuited for Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Or...rather I should say it's an approach\Nonly Naruto can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In that training...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,in a sense you might\Njust exceed me, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll...exceed you, Kakashi Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be with you the whole time\Non this training.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And it will be a different type of training...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What're we going to do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to create a Ninjutsu\Nof ultimate strength just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to learn a new Ninjutsu\Nthat will exceed the Rasengan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the acquisition\Nof such a power
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,will require an enormous amount\Nof time and effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get strong instantly\Nafter just a few days
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,like the hero in a novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's completely different from
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,being carefully taught\Nand learning a Jutsu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,like the Rasengan that\Nhas already been created.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,An enormous amount of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just said we don't have time!\NSasuke will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm saying is, I figured out a way\Nto do it in a short amount of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.09,0:10:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we do it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How're you doing, Kakashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuma Sensei, you could\Nat least knock!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why it's Naruto and Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your mission already...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that guy from back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who is he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is all of this happening\N{\i1}so suddenly today...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Relax. First, smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...for the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:11:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Akatsuki activity is finally\Ngetting into full swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,before they start churning things\Nup around the Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, this is a significant crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's also our chance\Nto attack them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just sit around anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.75,0:11:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's what was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I buy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Sai.\NPlease just call me by my first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, he's pretty cute...\NHe kind of resembles Sasuke, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,On the outside.\NBut he's quite different on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't really read the mood\Nof a room, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about Sasuke from\NLady Tsunade.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you guys out in the future\Nshould something happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:12:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finished with those troublesome\NChunin Exams, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You missed out on becoming\Na Chunin again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that was the least\Nof your problems, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing here\Nwith the whole gang in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a break room, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys go on ahead to "Barbe-Q."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys from Team Kakashi\Nshould go too if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Barbeque!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I second that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll sit next to Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to talk to Kakashi alone\Nabout a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The barbeque is on me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the rest of the discussion\Nabout my training?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll get to that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Later?! I'm really curious about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we can't start training while\NI'm still in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What took you so long, Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Where's Shikamaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he was going home because he has to get some horns for medicinal use with his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He always shows up\Nfor end-of-mission parties...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a first for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She isn't taking my advice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I'll eat Shikamaru's share!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Choji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to introduce ourselves\Nto Sai before we eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh...right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:14:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears things have started\Ngetting turbulent outside the land...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.16,0:14:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as their objective\Nis the Tailed Beasts,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a foregone conclusion that\Nthey'll target this village,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to leave me out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also concerned about\NAkatsuki developments.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Will Naruto...be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If those guys from the Akatsuki attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Gaara couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he probably won't be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}First meetings are very important\N{\i1}in order to quickly open up to people...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to decide on nicknames\N{\i1}and terms of endearment right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'm Choji Akimichi\Nof the Akimichi Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.\NUh, you're Sai, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.67,0:14:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you...uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Character trait...character trait...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's not going to say\N{\i1}that taboo word, is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai! "Fatty" is absolutely a taboo word\Nin front of Choji. Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he...\Nstart to say something just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It sure is tough coming up\N{\i1}with nicknames...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Ino Yamanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My family owns\Nthe Yamanaka Flower Shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the case of a girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}saying a character trait\N{\i1}just makes them angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In other words, if I say the opposite...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't do it, Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go, Sai!\N{\i1}Let her have it good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you...uh...\Npretty lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you say that when it's Ino?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Sakura!
